  "detailed_description": "Somewhere far in space ... on a hostile acid planet ... there is only one way to escape!<br>Break through the dangerous regions of the acid planet. <br>Fight \"Aciders\" and vicious fauna to escape the acid planet in our modern-classic FPS!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1212550/extras/c20e68466ce7f5ede66d38d649fba0b3.avif?t=1767975730\" width=600 height=162 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>9 square kilometers of playable open world<br></li><li>fifeteen types of enemies<br></li><li>classic retro brown aesthetic<br></li><li>two controllable vehicles (boat and a sliding vehicle)</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1212550/extras/9185bf9201d7cb1eb08a9992fec136b3.avif?t=1767975730\" width=600 height=144 /></span><br><br>The game contains retro graphics inspired by other FPS games from the late nineties / early 2000s, however, it uses the capabilities offered by modern game engines, such as large open spaces.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1212550/extras/d12833ea385ce29794a11feebd3241c7.avif?t=1767975730\" width=600 height=162 /></span><br><br>If you like old arcade FPS games, but you have already completed all the games of this kind known to you, this game is for you.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Previews</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>E1M1 Magazine - Issue #4 \"feels like a true labour of love\" <br></li><li>View early demo Curator reviews: </li></ul>",
